parameters.name: CollectionName
parameters.description: The name of the geofence collection.

nested_items.name: CollectionName
nested_items.description: The name of the geofence collection.

nested_items.name: CollectionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the geofence collection resource. Used when you need to specify a resource across all Amazon Web Services.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The optional description for the geofence collection.

nested_items.name: PricingPlan
nested_items.description: No longer used. Always returns RequestBasedUsage.

nested_items.name: PricingPlanDataSource
nested_items.description: No longer used. Always returns an empty string.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyId
nested_items.description: A key identifier for an Amazon Web Services KMS customer managed key assigned to the Amazon Location resource.

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the geofence resource was created in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: UpdateTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the geofence collection was last updated in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ.

nested_items.name: GeofenceCount
nested_items.description: The number of geofences in the geofence collection.
